sequenceDiagram
  participant App
  participant OpenClix
  participant Scheduler as Local Scheduler

  App->>OpenClix: ingestEvent(user_signed_up)
  OpenClix->>OpenClix: Enroll campaign + evaluate eligibility
  OpenClix->>Scheduler: Schedule gentle-first-value-nudge (window+jitter)
  Scheduler-->>OpenClix: delivered event (tracked)
  OpenClix->>Scheduler: Chain next-day-value-reminder
  App->>OpenClix: ingestEvent(first_value_completed)
  OpenClix->>Scheduler: Cancel pending activation messages
